column5: I believe they got charged for that!!! Looks good on them morons.   P.S - That wasn't Johnny Knoxville.

Every time this gets posted half the field squaks about how stupid and disrespectful it is, half the field admits to laughing.  As disrespectful as it may be, its funny.  I worked at BPS up until last month and I would have laughed if that happened.
they where  just looking for the local indoor swimming pool and got lost.
No different than fishing in the lobster tank at the grocery store..  Tell me I'm not the only one who did that?
Disrespectful? absolutely Stupid? absolutely  Funny as hell? DEFINATELY
